    </div>
    
   
    <div class="container margin-donator">
        <h1 class="text-color-red">Process</h1>
        <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p class="mb-0">If you want to donate blood, please login/create account on my site bloodghar.com .
                we are provide two process for donate blood.
        </blockquote>
        
        <blockquote>
            <p class="mb-0">
                <ol>
                    <li>
                       If any emergency case hospital can't arrange blood, and the human who can't afford blood,
                       in that case hospital/human can post her/him problem and blood group on bloodghar.com, In
                       a few second we notified nearest person who want to help her/him. 
                    </li>
                    <li>
                       We have also provide a location of blood donor camp near you
                    </li>
                </ol>
        </blockquote>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="container margin-donator">
        <h1 class="text-color-red">Eligibility</h1>
        <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p class="mb-0">Thank you for  helping to donate with bloodghar.com . Please read the guidelines to ensure
                you are ready to donate. Your donation can save up to  life and you are sure to get that amazing
                feeling of accomplishment and satisfaction for helping.
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
            <stong class="text25 text-color-red unederline-red">Consider donating blood if :</h3>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote >
            <p class="mb-0">
                <ol>
                    
                    <li>
                        Donor must be at least 18 years age and minimum weight of 50Kg to donate blood.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Once in 3 months a donor can donate blood.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        This means on your last donation of blood there should be a minimum gap of 120 days.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Without any irregularities Pulse rate must be between 50 to 100 mm.
                    </li>
                </ol>
        </blockquote>
        
        
        <blockquote>
            <stong class="text25 text-color-red unederline-red">Not eligibility for donating blood :</h3>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote >
            <p class="mb-0">
                <ol>
                    
                    <li>
                        Hepatitis: You may not donate if you've been exposed to hepatitis in the last 12 months.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Pregnancy: when you?re pregnant, you may not donate blood.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Malaria: Any person suffering or have suffered from malaria cannot donate blood for at least 3 years.
                    </li>
                    
                </ol>
        </blockquote>
        
        <div class="container margin-donator">
        <h1 class="text-color-red">Important Note</h1>
        <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p class="mb-0">A person between 18 and 60 years, weighing 50kg or more can safely donate one unit of blood,
                that is, 350 ml once every three months. The blood volume can be recovered within
                24 hours after donation and the haemoglobin count returns to normal within two weeks.
        </blockquote>
        
        <blockquote>
            <p class="mb-0">
                <ol>
                    --if you have any questions about whether you qualify to donate, please talk to a donor care/doctor. 
                    
                </ol>
        </blockquote>
